Sanofi Wins U.S. Court Ruling Maintaining Eloxatin Exclusivity

-- B y   P h i l   S e r a f i n o
-- 
2011-09-19T05:04:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/sanofi-wins-u-s-court-ruling-maintaining-eloxatin-exclusivity.html
Sanofi said a federal judge in  New
Jersey  ruled in the company’s favor in a contractual dispute
arising from the resolution of the Eloxatin patent litigation.  The judge ruled against  Sun Pharmaceutical Industries Ltd. (SUNP) 
in a decision that maintains Eloxatin’s market exclusivity
through Aug. 9, 2012, Sanofi said in a statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Phil Serafino at 
 pserafino@bloomberg.net  